data.description: Welcome to 110 Blue Springs Way, a delightful two-story home with an unfinished basement, ready for a new owner to discover its potential. This residence offers a generous 2,240 square feet of living space, along with an additional 920 square feet in the basement. With 4 bedrooms and 2.5 bathrooms, this home is designed to provide comfort and convenience. Upon entry, you'll be greeted by a spacious dining room with large windows that offer a pleasing view of the front yard. The well-appointed kitchen features an island and flows seamlessly into the open-concept living room. Step outside from the kitchen onto the upper deck, overlooking your fenced-in yard, creating the ideal space for outdoor enjoyment. Moving upstairs, you'll discover a generously sized primary bedroom, complete with an en-suite bathroom, walk-in closet, double sinks, and a water closet. Additionally, there are three more roomy bedrooms, a full bathroom with double sinks, and a convenient walk-in laundry room. The unfinished walkout basement holds substantial potential. The sellers have thoughtfully started the process by insulating certain areas and adding electrical outlets. The backyard offers ample space and privacy, enclosed by a fence. One side of the property benefits from added seclusion, thanks to a detention pond located between properties. Plus, there are no homes directly behind, creating a tranquil environment. This property is full of promise and ready for you to make it your own.  USDA Financing eligable.
